<p><strong>七月七日天河配，牛郎织女来相会</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/22f0a505268d4840b3a661c0e4f05012.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛郎织女遥遥相望一载</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只为七夕的鹊桥相会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这段动人的故事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寄托了世人对爱的期许</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">护佑着平凡日子中的每一次心动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 也承载了无数满怀憧憬的山盟海誓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在磴山喜鹊谷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同样有着一座“鹊桥”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们纷纷在上面锁上“同心锁”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将彼此的爱“牢牢锁住” </p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200822/a0af83c813ec439eb4d9432e9a56b366.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
